      "text": "……ふふ、懐かしいわぁ",
      "startTime": 2.1666667025,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "レッスンお疲れ様\n何を見ているんだ？",
      "startTime": 8.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_01-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "昔出演した、音楽番組の動画です\nちょっと見返したくなってなぁ",
      "startTime": 13.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "出演したって……優個人でか？",
      "startTime": 16.4565304954,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_01-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "トリエルの三人に決まってるやんか\nうちらはデビューした時から三人一緒や",
      "startTime": 23.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_01-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "こん時のうちらは、まだまだ甘ちゃんやってん\n笑顔もトークもぎこちなくてなぁ",
      "startTime": 30.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_01-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "ほら、今、うちがセリフを盛大に噛んだやろ？\nこういう失敗を二度とせんように時々見返してるんよ",
      "startTime": 37.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そうか。なら、ちょうど良かったかもな",
      "startTime": 42.8397273897,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "優が見てた関東ローカルの音楽番組なんだが\n実は、終了することが決定したそうだ",
      "startTime": 50.0701812115,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_09_01-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "え、それほんまなん！？\n初めて出演した番組やから、ちょっと寂しいなぁ……",
